        {
            "id": 6007131,
            "title": "特斯拉5月德國銷量繼續下滑",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>德國道路交通管理局 KBA 周三 (4 日) 表示，雖然電動車整體銷量有所成長，但特斯拉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSLA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSLA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSLA-US</a>) 的 5 月德國銷量下降了三分之一。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007131%2Fl%2Ff61c7b992c4063b32ba31a0bff229da7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">特斯拉5月德國銷量繼續下滑。（圖：REUTERS/TPG）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>KBA 表示，特斯拉 5 月在德國銷售了 1210 輛車，年減 36.2%；而新註冊的電動車總數則成長了 44.9%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>由於歐洲消費者購買更多中國電動車，以及一些人抗議執行長馬斯克的政治活動，這家汽車製造商在多個歐洲市場的銷量連續第 5 個月下滑。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>該德國機構表示，中國電動車製造商比亞迪 (BYDDY-US)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1211-HK</a>) 5 月銷量成長了 8 倍，達到 1857 輛。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
